00:17:54,470 --> 00:17:58,840
Blue Gilly kicked some guys' ass again!

254
00:18:00,260 --> 00:18:05,100
I think you can't protect your king
with such weak soldiers.

255
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:15,140
Looks like he has spirit.

256
00:18:15,320 --> 00:18:20,580
Oh, in the meantime,
Abdullah and Tank are facing each other!

257
00:18:38,120 --> 00:18:39,060
What the...

258
00:18:49,310 --> 00:18:53,600
I-I can't believe it!
They're taking down Tank!

259
00:18:54,600 --> 00:18:56,870
The military captain of
Dressrosa's Self-Defense Army -

260
00:18:56,870 --> 00:19:00,180
Tank Lepant got eliminated!

261
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:05,120
He fell a prey to the pair of evils -
Abdullah and Jeet!

262
00:19:05,360 --> 00:19:07,700
They keep using dirty tricks!

263
00:19:08,250 --> 00:19:09,820
Captain Tank!

264
00:19:10,210 --> 00:19:13,750
Over a 100 competitors have been eliminated

265
00:19:13,750 --> 00:19:17,100
and there are only 30 some
men left in the ring!

266
00:19:18,890 --> 00:19:20,360
A little more to go.

267
00:19:20,360 --> 00:19:22,510
It doesn't matter how tough
the remaining one will be

268
00:19:22,510 --> 00:19:24,220
as long as we have the King Punch...

269
00:19:25,860 --> 00:19:28,200
Competitors led by Dagama, the tactician,

270
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:31,860
are protecting Elizabello II,
the king of Prodence Kingdom!

271
00:19:32,380 --> 00:19:37,660
When is he going to throw
the devastating King Punch?!

272
00:19:38,610 --> 00:19:40,410
Who's next?!

273
00:19:40,870 --> 00:19:44,500
Those who wish to bleed, come fight us!

274
00:19:44,690 --> 00:19:47,340
The pair of evils - Abdullah and Jeet

275
00:19:47,340 --> 00:19:49,870
who took down the strong man - Lepant,

276
00:19:49,870 --> 00:19:53,100
are trying to provoke their next victim!

277
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:01,250
What?!

278
00:20:14,010 --> 00:20:15,810
Bellamy!

279
00:20:16,060 --> 00:20:17,600
Bellamy-sama!

280
00:20:18,170 --> 00:20:20,590
"Atrocious"! "Evil"!

281
00:20:20,590 --> 00:20:24,640
Those are the words only fitting to this man!

282
00:20:25,060 --> 00:20:30,580
Is he the top contender to
beat Elizabello II after all?!

283
00:20:36,130 --> 00:20:41,150
In the meantime,
the Jiaokungdo martial artist - Blue Gilly

284
00:20:41,460 --> 00:20:43,450
and the mysterious gladiator - Ricky,

285
00:20:43,450 --> 00:20:46,460
the two strong men are fighting each other!

286
00:20:49,430 --> 00:20:52,000
That Fish-Man is so tough!

287
00:20:52,390 --> 00:20:55,350
He's been knocking out all of his
opponents with a single blow!

288
00:20:55,350 --> 00:20:56,820
That's so cool!

289
00:20:58,080 --> 00:20:59,300
I'm so excited!

290
00:21:04,980 --> 00:21:10,680
It seems like one of these competitors
is likely to win Block B!

291
00:21:15,840 --> 00:21:17,120
Stop him!

292
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:19,360
Unbelievable!

293
00:21:19,370 --> 00:21:24,160
How much more does Bartolomeo
want to offend other people?!

294
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:26,900
Why is nobody kicking his ass?!

295
00:21:28,550 --> 00:21:31,540
In front of this huge audience,

296
00:21:31,550 --> 00:21:35,240
