297
00:21:35,620 --> 00:21:39,440
No one has ever done such a thing
in this Colosseum!

298
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:44,220
It feels so good!

299
00:21:44,670 --> 00:21:49,780
Somebody, stop him!

300
00:21:53,450 --> 00:21:55,710
Here comes that somebody!

301
00:21:55,710 --> 00:21:58,880
Some of us are taking this
thing seriously, brat!

302
00:21:58,880 --> 00:21:59,860
What?

303
00:22:00,230 --> 00:22:04,200
You'll have to excuse me
for attacking you from behind!

304
00:22:04,950 --> 00:22:09,440
Hey, wait! I'm not even
ready to fight back! Hey...

305
00:22:09,460 --> 00:22:14,250
The hero who came in to punish him is
the Fish-Man warrior - Hack!

306
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:19,050
4000 Brick...

307
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:23,090
Do it! Kick his ass, Hack!

308
00:22:25,740 --> 00:22:28,000
...Fist!

309
00:22:32,650 --> 00:22:33,870
He did it!

310
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:47,740
Just kidding!

311
00:22:59,310 --> 00:23:03,030
What did he do?!
Hack is the one who collapsed!

312
00:23:03,330 --> 00:23:05,140
What's going on?!

313
00:23:06,080 --> 00:23:08,130
What was that?

314
00:23:08,150 --> 00:23:11,880
Wh-What kind of monster are you?!

315
00:23:11,880 --> 00:23:14,410
Bartolomeo!
